<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Me & David Ortiz</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2244019899/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Me & David Ortiz" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2136/2244019899_45b0e6825d_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>I finally have photographic proof that I met David Ortiz at CES.</p>

<p>Because my camera was <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2174085749/in/set-72157603653437828/">a tad busted</a>, the folks behind me in line offered to take my photo with their camera, then email me the photo.  It arrived last night, so now you can all see evidence of the strong personal friendship me &amp; Papi share.</p>

<p>(I'm the one on the right)</p>
        </p>

