<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/jan/10/">&#x27a0;</a> January 10, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="squeezebox-duet-network" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.slimdevices.com/pi_duet.html">Squeezebox Duet Network Music System</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>The new Squeezebox hardware was one of the best things I saw at CES.  The remote is pretty nice, but the best thing is that, like their SlimServer software, the firmware is open-source and Lua-based, so &#8220;the community&#8221; can write plugins and features for the remote.  I predict this&#8217;ll be huge.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
                    Filed under
                    
