<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Plen</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2176177957/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Plen" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2244/2176177957_bea1d0d07b_m.jpg" height="240" width="180" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>I was excited to see Plen, since he's a true celebrity -- Last night on The Amazing Race, one of the choices on the detour involved controlling Plens with cellphones and trying to score goals.</p>

<p><a href="http://plen.jp/">plen.jp/</a></p>
        </p>

