        <h4>Versus Scoreboard</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2176176185/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Versus Scoreboard" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2084/2176176185_338dde9c07_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>Portable boombox-type-thing with remote-controlled score displays, a countdown timer, etc.</p>

<p>It sounds a bit gimmicky and crappy, but it's something I desperately wanted a few years back when doing improv.  I could definitely see Theatersports or Comedysportz troupes using it for away gigs.</p>

<p><a href="http://www.versusscoreboard.com/">www.versusscoreboard.com/</a></p>
